snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Retail Announcement - Skybound Games
snippet.description:
Slime Rancher is coming to retail on PlayStation 4 and Xbox! Explore the Far, Far Range with the new boxed edition of Slime Rancher on PS4 and Xbox One this September!

Available September 2018! 

Developed by Monomi Park
www.slimerancher.com
www.monomipark.com
Follow us on Twitter: @monomipark

Retail release published by Skybound Games
www.skyboundgames.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SkyboundGames/
Twitter: @SkyboundGames
